OL,3,CSouthport victim's aunt speaks of
OL,4,Cfamily's 'immense' pain
OL,6,FThe aunt of nine-year-old Alice
OL,7,FDaSilva Aguiar, who was killed in the
OL,8,FSouthport stabbing attack, has spoken
OL,9,Fof the family's "immense pain".
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News in Madeira,
OL,12,FAlbertina Freitas said: "My brother-in-
OL,13,Flaw is in such a state that he can't
OL,14,Feven talk to the family. We try to
OL,15,Ftalk to him, but he doesn't want to.
OL,16,FHe just clings to the girl's things.
OL,18,F"We are not going through it directly,
OL,19,Fbut we can imagine the pain my brother
OL,20,Fis experiencing. It is an immense
OL,21,Fpain."
