OL,6,FAlice was killed while attending a
OL,7,FTaylor Swift holiday workshop on
OL,8,FMonday morning in Hart Street,
OL,9,FSouthport. Six-year-old Bebe King and
OL,10,Fseven-year-old Elsie Dot Stancombe
OL,11,Fwere also fatally injured.
OL,13,FEight other children suffered knife
OL,14,Fwounds ` five of whom are in a
OL,15,Fcritical condition - and two adults
OL,16,Fwere also critically hurt in the
OL,17,Fattack.
