OL,3,CSouthport victim's aunt speaks of
OL,4,Cfamily's 'immense' pain
OL,6,FAlbertina added: "Nobody expected
OL,7,Fthis, especially the way it
OL,8,Fhappened...Nobody can really be
OL,9,Fprepared for something like this. This
OL,10,Ftragedy that happened to our girl...
OL,11,Fit's so painful."
OL,13,FOf her sister, Alice's mother, she
OL,14,Fadded: "She doesn't speak at all".
OL,16,FThe family are planning a mass service
OL,17,Fon Saturday at Quinta Grande Church in
OL,18,FMadeira, where they plan to release
OL,19,Fballoons, wearing t-shirts with
OL,20,FAlice's photo printed on it.
