OL,6,FAlbertina shared that Alice's
OL,7,Fgrandparents were offered flights to
OL,8,Fthe UK by the Portuguese Consulate to
OL,9,Fattend her funeral.
OL,11,F'Wherever she is, she is a little
OL,12,Fangel,' says former neighbour Olivia
OL,13,FBatista.
OL,15,FOlivia Batista was a friend and
OL,16,Fneighbour of Alice's parents when they
OL,17,Flived in Madeira. Speaking to ITV News
OL,18,Fshe said the whole village is in shock.
