OL,6,FShe decribed Alice as a "little Angel"
OL,7,Fstill at school. She added: "We all
OL,8,Ffeel the pain, there are no words. We
OL,9,Fare all suffering after what happened".
OL,11,F'I hope Alice continues her dance in
OL,12,Fheaven,' says local Parish Priest,
OL,13,FPedro Nobrega.
OL,15,FPedro Nobrega, is the Priest of the
OL,16,Flocal Quinta Grande Parish. He told
OL,17,FITV News that dedicated services have
OL,18,Fbeen held for Alice at the church
OL,19,Fwhich her distressed grandmother
OL,20,Fattended.
