OL,6,FHe said it was important not to give
OL,7,Fup and to lead a life Alice would have
OL,8,Fwanted her family and loved ones to
OL,9,Flive. He said that in these unexpcted
OL,10,Fmoments of tragedy it was imporant to
OL,11,Fhold onto all the goodness people
OL,12,Fleave behind.
OL,14,FEarlier in the week, Alice's mother
OL,15,Fand father paid tribute to their
OL,16,Fdaughter and said: "Keep smiling and
OL,17,Fdancing like you love to do our
OL,18,FPrincess, like we said before to you,
OL,19,Fyou're always our princess and no one
OL,20,Fwould change that. Love from Your Hero
OL,21,FDaddy and Mummy."
