OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy, who cannot be named
OL,7,Ffor legal reasons, remains in custody
OL,8,Faccused of murder and attempted murder
OL,9,Ffollowing the incident.
OL,11,FIn a statement released on Tuesday,
OL,12,FBebe King's family said: "No words can
OL,13,Fdescribe the devastation that has hit
OL,14,Four family as we try to deal with the
OL,15,Floss of our little girl Bebe."
OL,17,FJenni Stancombe, Elsie's mother, took
OL,18,Fto social media after disorder broke
OL,19,Fout on Tuesday night in response to
OL,20,Fthe attack.
